### Patterns

Pattern | Description
------- | -----------
`%s%` | Matched with any but `/`
`%i%` | Matched with any numbers.
`%f%` | Matched with any numbers and floats.
`%*%` | Matched with any and `/`
`%[foo,bar,baz\,qux]%` | Matched with `foo`, `bar` and `baz,qux`
`%[foo,bar,%i%]%` | Matched with `foo`, `bar` and any numbers.

